pull_request.title: CPU feature optimizing copy_from_pqclean v2/rebased
pull_request.body:
This is a new, clean (no copied files included) iteration of PR #675,
- eliminating "clean" (C-only) implementation copy warnings
- tested OK after removing all previous PQClean copies
- tested OK with cmake build option combinations make/ninja, static/shared, Debug/Optimized

Actual performance improvements become visible only after PR #683 is merged.
